Forked at commit d71068a (after upstream v0.6.1) and substantially
extended. Original code is licensed under the MIT License; see LICENSE.

Notable changes since fork point:
- Performance: TUI startup ~80x faster, refresh ~2x faster
- Interactive sidebar dock with mini sprites
- Sprite names, collision-avoidance, rename UI
- Keybindings: g (lazygit), d (diffnav), D (dash)
- Renamed from "recon" to "roostr" to mark divergence

Configuration paths and binary name changed:
- ~/.config/recon/  →  ~/.config/roostr/
- ~/.cache/recon/   →  ~/.cache/roostr/
- ~/.cargo/bin/recon → ~/.cargo/bin/roostr
Run `cargo uninstall recon` before installing roostr if upgrading.
